---
layout: base.njk
title: About
---

<!-- Terminal Header with whoami command -->
<section class="mb-12">
  <div class="terminal-window bg-terminal-surface border border-terminal-border rounded-lg overflow-hidden max-w-2xl mx-auto shadow-lg">
    <div class="terminal-chrome bg-terminal-darker px-4 py-3 flex items-center gap-2 border-b border-terminal-border">
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500/80"></div>
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500/80"></div>
      <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500/80"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="terminal-body p-6 md:p-8 font-mono">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-terminal-light-surface mb-4">
        <span class="text-terminal-green">$</span>
        <span>whoami</span>
      </div>
      <div class="text-terminal-green text-lg mb-4">{{ site.author }}</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Avatar and Bio Section -->
<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16" data-reveal>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 items-start">
    <!-- Avatar -->
    <div class="md:col-span-1 flex justify-center md:justify-start">
      <div class="w-48 h-48 md:w-40 md:h-40 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-br from-terminal-green to-terminal-cyan text-terminal-darker flex items-center justify-center text-white text-6xl md:text-5xl font-bold shadow-lg border-4 border-terminal-border">
        {{ site.author | first | upper }}
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Bio -->
    <div class="md:col-span-2">
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-terminal-light-surface mb-4 font-mono">
        <span class="text-terminal-green">→</span> About cosmic
      </h1>
      
      <div class="space-y-4 text-terminal-dim text-lg leading-relaxed">
        <p>
          A software engineer and creative technologist from the digital frontier. I spend my days crafting elegant code and my nights exploring the intersection of technology, design, and storytelling.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          When I'm not debugging or shipping features, you'll find me behind a camera lens exploring the beauty of the mundane. Photography is my meditation—a way to pause and frame the world differently.
        </p>
        
        <p>
          Welcome to my corner of the web. Here you'll find essays on code, life lessons learned through building, and visual stories through photography.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Interests Grid -->
<section class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-16" data-reveal>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-8">
    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-terminal-light-surface font-mono">
      <span class="text-terminal-cyan">→</span> Interests
    </h2>
    <div class="flex-1 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-terminal-border to-transparent"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
    <!-- Interest Cards -->
    <div class="bg-terminal-surface border border-terminal-border rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-terminal-green/50 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-green text-xl">◆</span>
        <h3 class="text-terminal-light-surface font-mono font-semibold">Full-Stack Development</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-terminal-dim text-sm">Building scalable systems from frontend to backend, with a passion for clean code and architecture.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-terminal-surface border border-terminal-border rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-terminal-cyan/50 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-cyan text-xl">◆</span>
        <h3 class="text-terminal-light-surface font-mono font-semibold">Digital Photography</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-terminal-dim text-sm">Capturing light and moments through the lens. Street, landscape, and documentary photography.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-terminal-surface border border-terminal-border rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-terminal-green/50 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-green text-xl">◆</span>
        <h3 class="text-terminal-light-surface font-mono font-semibold">Open Source</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-terminal-dim text-sm">Contributing to the community and building tools that help developers ship faster and better.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-terminal-surface border border-terminal-border rounded-lg p-4 hover:border-terminal-cyan/50 transition-colors">
      <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mb-2">
        <span class="text-terminal-cyan text-xl">◆</span>
        <h3 class="text-terminal-light-surface font-mono font-semibold">Web Performance</h3>
      </div>
      <p class="text-terminal-dim text-sm">Obsessed with fast, responsive experiences. Optimizing for humans first, metrics second.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

