    </p>
    <a href="mailto:hello@cosmic.dev" class="inline-block bg-terminal-green text-terminal-dark hover:bg-terminal-green/90 font-mono font-medium px-8 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors">
      Say Hello
    </a>
  </div>
</section>
